    p.
        Angular Seed Advanced is a starter project that implements best practices in coding, building and testing Angular 2 apps.
        Additionally it adds various enhancements and integrations for large global projects.

    p This view was built from a Pug template.

    h2 Features

    ul
        li Ready to go, statically typed build system using Gulp for working with TypeScript.
        li Production and development builds.
        li Sample unit tests with Jasmine and Karma including code coverage via Istanbul.
        li End-to-end tests with Protractor.
        li Development server with live reload.
        li TypeScript definition management using Typings.
        li Basic Service Worker, which implements "Cache then network strategy".
        li Integration with <a href="https://lodash.com/" target="blank">lodash</a>.
        li RxJS powered state management (Redux) via <a href="https://github.com/ngrx/store" target="blank">ngrx/store</a>.
        li i18n with <a href="https://github.com/ocombe/ng2-translate" target="blank">ng2-translate</a>.
        li Native cross platform app development with <a href="https://www.nativescript.org/" target="blank">NativeScript</a>.
